name: Silent Rain
description: Raindrops on the steel, the strike cuts through the shower, only silence left.

name: Frozen Whisper
description: Frozen blade of glass, shards of time in every cut, winter breath stands still.

name: Moonlit Tide
description: Rising, falling tides, the sword hums with ocean’s pull, moonlight splits the deep.

name: Vanishing Mist
description: Mist upon the steel, vanishing with every swing, shadows learn to hide.

name: Dawnflame
description: Blinding arc of flame, one strike carries dawn itself, darkness breaks apart.

name: Molten Path
description: Molten veins awake, burning paths where fury flows, stone remembers fire.

name: Ashen Dream
description: Ash drifts on the breeze, quiet end of raging storms, embers dream of flame.

name: Crimson Dance
description: Dancing sparks alive, the sword sings in crackling tongues, all becomes consumed.

name: Heartroot
description: Roots entwine the edge, ancient pulse beneath the ground, life defends its core.

name: Verdant Infinity
description: Soft and evergreen, blade rests where the forest breathes, silence guards the moss.

name: Echoing Vale
description: Between hills it sleeps, echoes bloom from strike to strike, peace beneath the stone.

name: Iron Peak
description: Unyielding summit, steel becomes the peak itself, echo of the sky.

name: Stormsong
description: Whispers on the edge, a single stroke bends the air, storm is born in flight.

name: Petalwind
description: Gentle morning wind, each cut scatters petals wide, spring awakens soft.

name: Hollow Whisp
description: One note carries far, steel resounds in hollow cliffs, silence answers back.

name: Shifting Veil
description: Shifting, drifting veil, hidden strike behind the gray, light escapes the shroud.

name: Living Pulse
description: Breath within the steel, every strike affirms the pulse, being sings in light.

name: Final Path
description: Stillness after war, the blade knows the final path, all returns to void.

name: Blossomfang
description: Leaves entwine the hilt, petals scatter with each step, spring is held in steel.

name: Feral Spirit
description: Footsteps in the wild, fang and claw reflect in steel, hunt within the cut.

name: Start of Spring
description: Ice breaks, ripples bloom, silver fins kiss newborn light, spring stirs in the lake.

name: Rain Water
description: Soft rains veil the shore, otters dance through silver waves, life stirs with the flood.

name: Awakening of Insects
description: Thunder splits the sky, earth trembles, sleep breaks to song, insects greet the storm.

name: Vernal Equinox
description: Day and night embrace, swallows weave the sky with wings, balance fills the air.

name: Clear and Bright
description: Paulownia blooms, rainbows arch through crystal skies, spring breathes, pure and bright.

name: Grain Rain
description: Gentle grain rains fall, peonies crown fields with grace, ginger scents the earth.

name: Start of Summer
description: Peach blush meets warm sun, tender shoots rise from the soil, summer takes its breath.

name: Grain Full
description: Plump grains bow with weight, litchi ripens, red and sweet, summer hums with life.

name: Grain in Ear
description: Golden fields now sing, barley whispers to the wind, summer’s crown takes shape.

name: Summer Solstice
description: Sun reigns high and long, watermelon cools the heat, light overflows earth.

name: Minor Heat
description: Papaya ripens, summer whispers through hot breeze, sunlight drips like gold.

name: Major Heat
description: Blazing sun above, fireflies flicker through the heat, summer hums in gold.

name: Start of Autumn
description: Autumn breeze arrives, longan hangs in golden clusters, summer fades to gold.

name: Limit of Heat
description: Bamboo shoots emerge, heat wanes beneath autumn skies, season shifts in green.

name: White Dew
description: Morning dew clings soft, pitaya and taro gleam, autumn chills the earth.

name: Autumnal Equinox
description: Day and night balance, pear and green onion flourish, autumn breathes in calm.

name: Cold Dew
description: Cold dew coats the ground, lotus roots lie in still waters, geese have flown afar.

name: Frost Descent
description: Frost glazes the earth, persimmons glow, yams slumber, autumn whispers chill.

name: Start of Winter
description: Sugar-apples hide, winter winds bite at bare trees, frost creeps through the land.

name: Minor Snow
description: Light snow dusts the field, grapes cling to the vine with frost, cabbage guards the cold.

name: Major Snow
description: Heavy snow descends, cabbage shelters from the white, kumquats gleam like fire.

name: Winter Solstice
description: Longest night enfolds, deer shed antlers in the frost, tangyuan warms hearts.

name: Minor Cold
description: Magpies build their nests, crown daisies brave the cold wind, winter whispers mild.

name: Major Cold
description: Falcon sweeps the sky, ice grips ponds in hardened sheets, radishes endure.

name: Verdant Oath
description: Rivers through dry stone,the dragon awakens rain, spring returns with oath.

name: Ashen Rebirth
description: Ashes drift skyward, a lone feather births the flame, rebirth takes its wing.

name: Iron Roar
description: Thunder splits the peak, silent stars awake below, a roar caged in steel.

name: Still Waters Deep
description: Frozen lake lies still, serpent dreams in endless depths, time sleeps in the blade.

name: Moonlit Farewell
description: Moonlight in bamboo, a child of heaven descends, earth cradles her glow.

name: Celestial Descent
description: Petals fall in vain, emperors and poets dream, her heart drifts moonward.

name: Bamboo Cradle
description: Eventually, Kaguya-hime returned to the Moon.

name: Tears of the Emperor
description: Moonlit steel remains, whispering her fleeting grace, memory made blade.

name: Bridge of Magpies
description: Stars weave threads of love, a cowherd’s gaze meets her eyes, heaven bends to earth.

name: Starry Veil
description: Heaven splits their path, river of stars flows between, love drifts far apart.

name: Rivers of Stars
description: Magpies span the stars, a fleeting bridge in the night, hearts meet once a year.

name: One Night Together
description: One night binds their hearts, under the starry river, love blooms, then drifts back.

name: Stormcutter
description: Exiled god descends, eight-headed shadow writhes fierce, land cries for his sword.

name: Eightfold Fang
description: Eight heads, eight long tails, writhing terror shakes the land, a storm of scales roars.

name: Sakeblade Offering
description: Sake lures the beast, one by one the heads fall swift, silence claims the flood.

name: Kusanagi's Echo
description: Dragon’s heart opens, within, a sword gleams with fate, Kusanagi shines.

name: Celestial Gourd
description: Eight lights traverse waves, mortal and divine entwined, evil bows to them.

name: Fan of the Immortal Lady
description: Eight lights traverse waves, mortal and divine entwined, evil bows to them.

name: Brush of Judgement

name: Blooming Lotus Blade
description: Eight lights traverse waves, mortal and divine entwined, evil bows to them.

name: Flask of the Drunken Immortal
description: Eight lights traverse waves, mortal and divine entwined, evil bows to them.

name: Dawnveil
description: Sun hides in shadow, cave swallows her golden light, world waits in silence.

name: Mirrorblade of Yata
description: Darkness cloaks the land, sunlight lost in hidden depths, earth trembles in night.

name: Cavebreaker
description: Laughter draws her out, gods dance beneath the bright sun, light returns once more.

name: Celebration of the Kami
description: From her radiant light, emperors trace their lineage, sun’s blood flows on earth.

name: Blade of the Peach Child
description: River-born he rises, peach cradles a noble heart, strength flows with the tide.

name: Kibi-Dango Oath
description: Peach boy treads the path, island shadows hide fierce fiends, hero’s step is firm.

name: Oni-Cleaver of Onigashima
description: Dog, monkey, and bird, loyal friends march by his side, fate shared on the road.

name: Banner of the Hero Boy
description: Together they strike, hearts and claws and wings as one, unity is power.
